import React from 'react'

import { Container, MessageList, MessageInputWrapper, MessageInput, MessageInputIcon } from './styles'

const ChannelData: React.FC = () => {
    return (
        <Container>

            <MessageList>
                <ChannelMessage                   
                    author="insanity"
                    date="2020/08/24"
                    content="have you seen all the UI clones I made?"
                />
                <ChannelMessage                   
                    author="insanity"
                    date="2020/08/25"
                    content="I also made a ton of work regarding back-end! Check it out!"
                />
            </MessageList>

            <MessageInputWrapper>
                <MessageInput type="text" placeholder="Message #chat-geral" />
                <MessageInputIcon />
            </MessageInputWrapper>

        </Container>
    )
}

export default ChannelData
